    },
    {
      "name": "data.relationalStore (ohos.data.relationalStore)",
      "purpose": "关系型数据库管理，基于SQLite提供完整SQL操作能力",
      "anchor": "ohosdatarelationalstore-关系型数据库",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "PersistentStorage",
      "purpose": "将AppStorage中的UI状态持久化到磁盘，应用重启后自动恢复",
      "anchor": "persistentstorage",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Environment (ArkUI environment)",
      "purpose": "查询设备系统环境变量（深浅色模式、语言、字号等），@Env装饰器读取窗口环境",
      "anchor": "environment-arkui-设备环境查询",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "Preferences 的 XML 模式下需手动调用 flush() 落盘；GSKV 模式（API 18+）实时落盘无需 flush",
    "PersistentStorage 是框架内置 API（无需 import），随 AppStorage 使用，API 12 起支持 null/undefined",
    "Environment.envProp 与 @Env 装饰器是两个独立机制：前者将系统环境变量存入 AppStorage；后者（API 22+）从 @kit.ArkUI 导入，直接在组件中读取窗口环境",
    "RelationalStore 单条数据建议不超过 2MB，单次查询建议不超过 5000 条"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

